wikipedia_page.main: Jamie Masson (born 5 April 1993) is a Scottish semi-professional footballer, who is currently with Cove Rangers. Masson has previously played for Aberdeen, Formartine United, Elgin City and Brechin City.

response: *Jamie Masson (born 1993): Scottish semi-professional footballer who has played for Aberdeen, Formartine United, Elgin City, Brechin City and other clubs.
